summary: This is an email exchange between US Attorney's Office personnel regarding a request for a legal briefing on pre-indictment delay that was filed in the Ghislaine Maxwell case. The email includes an attachment of the government's opposition to Maxwell's defense motions.
keyFacts: Email exchange dated April 9, 2021, regarding the Ghislaine Maxwell case.
Request for a legal briefing on pre-indictment delay filed in the Maxwell case.
Attachment includes the government's opposition to Maxwell's defense motions (dated February 26, 2021).
Correspondence is between personnel at the US Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York (USANYS).
